<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.2.10">
<l>eṭṭut ticaiyu meṇṇiṟan taperun tēvimār</l>
<l>viṭṭu viḷaṅka vīṟṟirun tavima laṉmalai</l>
<l>paṭṭip piṭikaḷ pakaṭuṟiñ cicceṉṟu mālaivāyt</l>
<l>teṭṭit tiḷaikkum teṉtiru māliruñ cōlaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain where the immaculate One is majestically enthroned</l>
<l rend="indent">while countless great goddesses shine,</l>
<l rend="indent">emitting [light] to the eight directions,</l>
<l>is Tirumāliruñcōlai in the south where unbridled female elephants,</l>
<l rend="indent">gone sniffing [out] the bulls,</l>
<l rend="indent">Sway to and fro, rubbing against [them] in the evening.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
